- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper uses a combination of Kalman filter and Hungarian algorithm for state estimation and data association.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper deals with developing an accurate and efficient system for real-time applications.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is unlikely as the paper does not mention any security or cryptography-related topics.
